    <title>Hexo Guide</title>
    <link href="/2019/11/26/hexo-guide/"/>
    <url>/2019/11/26/hexo-guide/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Start-Up"><a href="#Start-Up" class="headerlink" title="Start Up"></a>Start Up</h3><ul><li><p>run at local </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>deploy to github</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo clean &amp; hexo g &amp; hexo d<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="Write-a-new-article"><a href="#Write-a-new-article" class="headerlink" title="Write a new article"></a>Write a new article</h3><ul><li>Enter the project root directory,then type in the command:<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;新文章&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>hexo</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
